{"ID":"20230724011448-664ph06","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"icon":"1f4f3","id":"20230724011448-664ph06","scroll":"\u0026#123;\u0026quot;rootId\u0026quot;:\u0026quot;20230724011448-664ph06\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;startId\u0026quot;:\u0026quot;20230724011450-g4fllt3\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;endId\u0026quot;:\u0026quot;20230724011458-566l059\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;scrollTop\u0026quot;:0,\u0026quot;focusId\u0026quot;:\u0026quot;20230724011458-566l059\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;focusStart\u0026quot;:0,\u0026quot;focusEnd\u0026quot;:0\u0026#125;","title":"类型转换","updated":"20230724011458"},"Children":[{"ID":"20230724011450-g4fllt3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724011450-g4fllt3","updated":"20230724011450"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"1.当类型转换出现在表达式时，无论是unsigned还是signed的char和short都会被自动转换成int，如有必要会被转换成unsigned int（如果short与int的大小相同，unsigned short就比int大。这种情况下，unsigned short会被转换成unsigned int）。由于都是从较小类型转换为较大类型，所以这些转换被称为升级（promotion）。"}]},{"ID":"20230724011450-ny1egz0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724011450-ny1egz0","updated":"20230724011450"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"2.涉及两种类型的运算，两个值会被分别转换成两种类型的更高级别。"}]},{"ID":"20230724011450-8057duc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724011450-8057duc","updated":"20230724011450"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"3.类型的级别从高至低依次是long double、double、float、unsignedlong long、long long、unsigned long、long、unsigned int、int。例外的情况是，当 long 和 int 的大小相同时，unsigned int比long的级别高。之所以short和char类型没有列出，是因为它们已经被升级到int或unsigned int。"}]},{"ID":"20230724011450-eihka6l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724011450-eihka6l","updated":"20230724011450"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"4.在赋值表达式语句中，计算的最终结果会被转换成被赋值变量的类型。这个过程可能导致类型升级或降级（demotion）。所谓降级，是指把一种类型转换成更低级别的类型。"}]},{"ID":"20230724011450-dd8f9no","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724011450-dd8f9no","updated":"20230724011450"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"5.当作为函数参数传递时，char和short被转换成int，float被转换成double。"}]},{"ID":"20230724011458-566l059","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724011458-566l059"}}]}